# ─── Required: OpenAI (embeddings + answer generation) ───
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ─── Optional overrides ───
# Chat model used to generate cited answers.
OPENAI_CHAT_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
# Embedding model (1536-dim). text-embedding-3-large also works.
EMBEDDING_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This build runs fully on the single OPENAI_API_KEY above, using a local
# on-disk vector store (.data/store.json). No other services required.
#
# To deploy to a serverless host like Vercel (read-only filesystem), swap the
# local store for Supabase pgvector — see supabase/schema.sql and lib/store.ts.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
